<I c="Tutorial" i="tutorial" m="tutorials.tutorial" n="tutorial_EP21_ProjectGold_ScandalSecrets_Scandals" s="489302">
  <T n="category">488441<!--TutorialCategory: tutorial_Category_EP21_ProjectGold--></T>
  <T n="name">0x33D74EE3<!--String: "Scandals"--></T>
  <L n="slides">
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InEP21\UI\Tutorial\EP21_Lessons_Scandals1.png">2f7d0004:00000000:90094863ca5d2ccc</T>
      <T n="text">0x13B649D4<!--String: "If your Sim engages in questionable activity in front of other Sims, they may automatically be launched into a full blown <b><font color='#199C2C'>Scandal</font></b>. Additionally, if they're Extorted but don't pay up, they may have their <b><font color='#199C2C'>Secret Exposed</font></b> which will also trigger a Scandal. All the details related to active Scandals can be found in the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Notebook</font></b>, including time remaining, <b><font color='#199C2C'>Severity</font></b> consequences, and any <b><font color='#199C2C'>Complicit Sims</font></b> who are also impacted by the Scandal.\n\nWhile in a Scandal, Sims will experience negative social outcomes, reduced work performance, impacted Dynasty Prestige or Rank, and some Scandals will even have specific bonus effects. A Scandalized Sim will be followed around by a dark cloud, which can be turned off by selecting the Sim. The Scandals feature can also be disabled via <b><font color='#199C2C'>Game Options</font></b>."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InEP21\UI\Tutorial\EP21_Lessons_Scandals2.png">2f7d0004:00000000:90094863ca5d2ccf</T>
      <T n="text">0xD72CCE0F<!--String: "But it's not all doom and gloom! While in a Scandal, Sims can write a <b><font color='#199C2C'>Apology or Denial Statement</font></b> at the Computer to try and reduce the Scandal's impact, and certain Sims will even enjoy the extra attention.\n\nYour Sim can also choose to <b><font color='#199C2C'>Expose a Scandal</font></b> about another Sim, either because they failed to pay up when Extorted, to topple a Dynasty or Noble Rival, or even just to enjoy the drama. This can be done via social interactions, or on the Phone or PC."--></T>
    </U>
  </L>
  <L n="tags">
    <E>Lesson_EP21_ProjectGold_ScandalSecrets</E>
  </L>
